360001,94,745,75,90,1,81,10,Addasā kho bhagavā māgadhake paricārake‘‘ yaṃgatikā te bhavanto yaṃabhisamparāyā’’ ti. 
360002,94,745,91,103,1,119,12,Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito giñjakāvasathā nikkhamitvā vihārapacchāyāyaṃ paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
