360117,94,789,2,2,1,16,1,Bhāvitaiddhipādo 
360118,94,790,2,46,1,190,21,"287.‘‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññanti, bhonto devā tāvatiṃsā, yāva supaññattā cime tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena cattāro iddhipādā paññattā iddhipahutāya[ iddhibahulīkatāya( syā.)] iddhivisavitāya[ iddhivisevitāya( syā.)] iddhivikubbanatāya. "
360119,94,790,47,49,1,14,2,Katame cattāro? 
360120,94,790,50,56,1,77,6,Idha bho bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. 
360121,94,790,57,60,1,60,3,Vīriyasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. 
360122,94,790,61,64,1,59,3,Cittasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. 
360123,94,790,65,68,1,61,3,Vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. 
360124,94,790,69,86,1,142,15,"Ime kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena cattāro iddhipādā paññattā iddhipahutāya iddhivisavitāya iddhivikubbanatāya."
360125,94,791,2,25,1,157,20,"‘ ‘‘ Ye hi keci bho atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhosuṃ, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
360126,94,791,26,47,1,164,19,"Yepi hi keci bho anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhossanti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
360127,94,791,48,68,1,152,19,"Yepi hi keci bho etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhonti, sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā. "
360128,94,791,69,81,1,69,9,Passanti no bhonto devā tāvatiṃsā mamapimaṃ evarūpaṃ iddhānubhāvan’’ ti?
360129,94,791,82,89,1,18,3,‘‘ Evaṃ mahābrahme’’ ti.
360130,94,791,90,107,1,109,12,‘‘ Ahampi kho bho imesaṃyeva catunnañca iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā evaṃ mahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo’’ ti. 
