360133,94,792,2,3,1,20,2,Tividho okāsādhigamo 
360134,94,793,2,28,1,150,17,"288.‘‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññanti, bhonto devā tāvatiṃsā, yāvañcidaṃ tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena tayo okāsādhigamā anubuddhā sukhassādhigamāya. "
360135,94,793,29,31,1,11,2,Katame tayo? 
360136,94,793,32,41,1,70,9,Idha bho ekacco saṃsaṭṭho viharati kāmehi saṃsaṭṭho akusalehi dhammehi. 
360137,94,793,42,55,1,88,10,"So aparena samayena ariyadhammaṃ suṇāti, yoniso manasi karoti, dhammānudhammaṃ paṭipajjati. "
360138,94,793,56,67,1,130,11,So ariyadhammassavanaṃ āgamma yonisomanasikāraṃ dhammānudhammappaṭipattiṃ asaṃsaṭṭho viharati kāmehi asaṃsaṭṭho akusalehi dhammehi. 
360139,94,793,68,80,1,100,11,"Tassa asaṃsaṭṭhassa kāmehi asaṃsaṭṭhassa akusalehi dhammehi uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360140,94,793,81,115,1,149,18,"Seyyathāpi, bho, pamudā pāmojjaṃ[ pāmujjaṃ( pī. ka.)] jāyetha, evameva kho, bho, asaṃsaṭṭhassa kāmehi asaṃsaṭṭhassa akusalehi dhammehi uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360141,94,793,116,131,1,116,13,"Ayaṃ kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena paṭhamo okāsādhigamo anubuddho sukhassādhigamāya."
360142,94,794,2,25,1,162,17,"‘ ‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, bho, idhekaccassa oḷārikā kāyasaṅkhārā appaṭippassaddhā honti, oḷārikā vacīsaṅkhārā appaṭippassaddhā honti, oḷārikā cittasaṅkhārā appaṭippassaddhā honti. "
360143,94,794,26,38,1,88,10,"So aparena samayena ariyadhammaṃ suṇāti, yoniso manasi karoti, dhammānudhammaṃ paṭipajjati. "
360144,94,794,39,56,1,194,14,"Tassa ariyadhammassavanaṃ āgamma yonisomanasikāraṃ dhammānudhammappaṭipattiṃ oḷārikā kāyasaṅkhārā paṭippassambhanti, oḷārikā vacīsaṅkhārā paṭippassambhanti, oḷārikā cittasaṅkhārā paṭippassambhanti. "
360145,94,794,57,74,1,179,15,"Tassa oḷārikānaṃ kāyasaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā oḷārikānaṃ vacīsaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā oḷārikānaṃ cittasaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360146,94,794,75,101,1,228,22,"Seyyathāpi, bho, pamudā pāmojjaṃ jāyetha, evameva kho bho oḷārikānaṃ kāyasaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā oḷārikānaṃ vacīsaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā oḷārikānaṃ cittasaṅkhārānaṃ paṭippassaddhiyā uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360147,94,794,102,117,1,115,13,"Ayaṃ kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena dutiyo okāsādhigamo anubuddho sukhassādhigamāya."
360148,94,795,2,27,1,107,15,"‘ ‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, bho, idhekacco ‘ idaṃ kusalan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti,‘ idaṃ akusalan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
360149,94,795,28,51,1,143,18,"‘ Idaṃ sāvajjaṃ idaṃ anavajjaṃ, idaṃ sevitabbaṃ idaṃ na sevitabbaṃ, idaṃ hīnaṃ idaṃ paṇītaṃ, idaṃ kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
360150,94,795,52,64,1,88,10,"So aparena samayena ariyadhammaṃ suṇāti, yoniso manasi karoti, dhammānudhammaṃ paṭipajjati. "
360151,94,795,65,86,1,148,15,"So ariyadhammassavanaṃ āgamma yonisomanasikāraṃ dhammānudhammappaṭipattiṃ,‘ idaṃ kusalan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ idaṃ akusalan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
360152,94,795,87,109,1,140,18,"Idaṃ sāvajjaṃ idaṃ anavajjaṃ, idaṃ sevitabbaṃ idaṃ na sevitabbaṃ, idaṃ hīnaṃ idaṃ paṇītaṃ, idaṃ kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
360153,94,795,110,120,1,62,9,"Tassa evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato avijjā pahīyati, vijjā uppajjati. "
360154,94,795,121,130,1,70,8,"Tassa avijjāvirāgā vijjuppādā uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360155,94,795,131,153,1,119,15,"Seyyathāpi, bho, pamudā pāmojjaṃ jāyetha , evameva kho, bho, avijjāvirāgā vijjuppādā uppajjati sukhaṃ, sukhā bhiyyo somanassaṃ. "
360156,94,795,154,169,1,115,13,"Ayaṃ kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena tatiyo okāsādhigamo anubuddho sukhassādhigamāya. "
360157,94,795,170,190,1,115,14,"Ime kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena tayo okāsādhigamā anubuddhā sukhassādhigamāyā’’ ti. "
