360159,94,796,2,2,1,17,1,Catusatipaṭṭhānaṃ 
360160,94,797,2,30,1,163,19,"289.‘‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññanti, bhonto devā tāvatiṃsā, yāva supaññattā cime tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena cattāro satipaṭṭhānā paññattā kusalassādhigamāya. "
360161,94,797,31,33,1,14,2,Katame cattāro? 
360162,94,797,34,50,1,107,13,"Idha , bho, bhikkhu ajjhattaṃ kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
360163,94,797,51,61,1,79,9,"Ajjhattaṃ kāye kāyānupassī viharanto tattha sammā samādhiyati, sammā vippasīdati. "
360164,94,797,62,72,1,87,10,So tattha sammā samāhito sammā vippasanno bahiddhā parakāye ñāṇadassanaṃ abhinibbatteti. 
360165,94,797,73,84,1,94,9,Ajjhattaṃ vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati… pe… bahiddhā paravedanāsu ñāṇadassanaṃ abhinibbatteti. 
360166,94,797,85,96,1,87,9,Ajjhattaṃ citte cittānupassī viharati… pe… bahiddhā paracitte ñāṇadassanaṃ abhinibbatteti. 
360167,94,797,97,108,1,96,10,Ajjhattaṃ dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. 
360168,94,797,109,119,1,85,9,"Ajjhattaṃ dhammesu dhammānupassī viharanto tattha sammā samādhiyati, sammā vippasīdati. "
360169,94,797,120,130,1,91,10,So tattha sammā samāhito sammā vippasanno bahiddhā paradhammesu ñāṇadassanaṃ abhinibbatteti. 
360170,94,797,131,149,1,118,14,"Ime kho, bho, tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena cattāro satipaṭṭhānā paññattā kusalassādhigamāyā’’ ti. "
