360173,94,798,2,3,1,23,2,Satta samādhiparikkhārā 
360174,94,799,2,33,1,195,21,"290.‘‘‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññanti, bhonto devā tāvatiṃsā, yāva supaññattā cime tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena satta samādhiparikkhārā sammāsamādhissa paribhāvanāya sammāsamādhissa pāripūriyā. "
360175,94,799,34,36,1,12,2,Katame satta? 
360176,94,799,37,45,1,82,7,Sammādiṭṭhi sammāsaṅkappo sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo sammāvāyāmo sammāsati. 
360177,94,799,46,68,1,129,17,"Yā kho, bho, imehi sattahaṅgehi cittassa ekaggatā parikkhatā, ayaṃ vuccati, bho, ariyo sammāsamādhi saupaniso itipi saparikkhāro itipi. "
360178,94,799,69,82,1,107,10,"Sammādiṭṭhissa bho, sammāsaṅkappo pahoti, sammāsaṅkappassa sammāvācā pahoti, sammāvācassa sammākammanto pahoti. "
360179,94,799,83,107,1,199,18,"Sammākammantassa sammāājīvo pahoti, sammāājīvassa sammāvāyāmo pahoti, sammāvāyāmassa sammāsati pahoti , sammāsatissa sammāsamādhi pahoti, sammāsamādhissa sammāñāṇaṃ pahoti, sammāñāṇassa sammāvimutti pahoti. "
360180,94,799,108,116,1,36,6,"Yañhi taṃ, bho, sammā vadamāno vadeyya–"
360181,94,799,117,139,1,157,19,‘ svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhi apārutā amatassa dvārā’ ti idameva taṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya. 
360182,94,799,140,167,1,126,15,"Svākkhāto hi, bho, bhagavatā dhammo sandiṭṭhiko, akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhi apārutā amatassa dvārā[ dvārāti( syā. ka.)]."
360183,94,800,2,45,1,339,34,"‘ ‘‘ Ye hi keci, bho, buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgatā, dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgatā, saṅghe aveccappasādena samannāgatā, ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgatā , ye cime opapātikā dhammavinītā sātirekāni catuvīsatisatasahassāni māgadhakā paricārakā abbhatītā kālaṅkatā tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā. "
360184,94,800,46,49,1,27,3,Atthi cevettha sakadāgāmino.
360185,94,801,2,20,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Atthāyaṃ[ athāyaṃ( sī. syā.)] itarā pajā, puññābhāgāti me mano; "
360186,94,802,2,11,1,46,6,"Saṅkhātuṃ nopi sakkomi, musāvādassa ottappan’’ ti. "
360187,94,803,2,28,1,153,16,"291.‘ Imamatthaṃ, bhante, brahmā sanaṅkumāro bhāsittha, imamatthaṃ, bhante, brahmuno sanaṅkumārassa bhāsato vessavaṇassa mahārājassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi–"
360188,94,803,29,57,1,151,19,"‘‘ acchariyaṃ vata bho, abbhutaṃ vata bho, evarūpopi nāma uḷāro satthā bhavissati, evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ dhammakkhānaṃ, evarūpā uḷārā visesādhigamā paññāyissantī’’ ti. "
360189,94,803,58,71,1,118,11,"Atha, bhante, brahmā sanaṅkumāro vessavaṇassa mahārājassa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya vessavaṇaṃ mahārājānaṃ etadavoca–"
360190,94,803,72,95,1,155,19,"‘‘ taṃ kiṃ maññati bhavaṃ vessavaṇo mahārājā atītampi addhānaṃ evarūpo uḷāro satthā ahosi, evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ dhammakkhānaṃ, evarūpā uḷārā visesādhigamā paññāyiṃsu. "
360191,94,803,96,116,1,126,14,"Anāgatampi addhānaṃ evarūpo uḷāro satthā bhavissati, evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ dhammakkhānaṃ, evarūpā uḷārā visesādhigamā paññāyissantī’’’ ti. "
360192,94,804,2,47,1,208,22,"292.‘‘‘ Imamatthaṃ, bhante, brahmā sanaṅkumāro devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ abhāsi, imamatthaṃ vessavaṇo mahārājā brahmuno sanaṅkumārassa devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ bhāsato sammukhā sutaṃ[ sutvā( sī. pī.)] sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ sayaṃ parisāyaṃ ārocesi’’. "
360193,94,805,2,25,1,133,14,Imamatthaṃ janavasabho yakkho vessavaṇassa mahārājassa sayaṃ parisāyaṃ bhāsato sammukhā sutaṃ sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ[ paṭiggahetvā( sī. pī.)] bhagavato ārocesi. 
360194,94,805,26,53,1,250,25,"Imamatthaṃ bhagavā janavasabhassa yakkhassa sammukhā sutvā sammukhā paṭiggahetvā sāmañca abhiññāya āyasmato ānandassa ārocesi, imamatthamāyasmā ānando bhagavato sammukhā sutvā sammukhā paṭiggahetvā ārocesi bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ upāsakānaṃ upāsikānaṃ. "
360195,94,805,54,64,1,110,10,Tayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ iddhañceva phītañca vitthārikaṃ bāhujaññaṃ puthubhūtaṃ yāva devamanussehi suppakāsitanti. 
360196,94,806,2,5,1,36,3,Janavasabhasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ. 
360197,94,807,2,5,1,17,1,6. Mahāgovindasuttaṃ 
360198,94,808,2,21,1,71,10,293. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. 
360199,94,808,22,36,1,142,14,Atha kho pañcasikho gandhabbaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ gijjhakūṭaṃ pabbataṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
360200,94,808,37,42,1,55,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
360201,94,808,43,50,1,67,7,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho pañcasikho gandhabbaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
360202,94,808,51,72,1,100,14,"‘‘ yaṃ kho me, bhante, devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ sammukhā sutaṃ sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ, ārocemi taṃ bhagavato’’ ti."
360203,94,808,73,85,1,43,7,"‘‘ Ārocehi me tvaṃ, pañcasikhā’’ ti bhagavā avoca. "
360204,94,809,2,2,1,9,1,Devasabhā 
360205,94,810,2,29,1,178,19,"294.‘‘ Purimāni, bhante, divasāni purimatarāni tadahuposathe pannarase pavāraṇāya puṇṇāya puṇṇamāya rattiyā kevalakappā ca devā tāvatiṃsā sudhammāyaṃ sabhāyaṃ sannisinnā honti sannipatitā; "
360206,94,810,30,43,1,91,12,"mahatī ca dibbaparisā samantato nisinnā honti, cattāro ca mahārājāno catuddisā nisinnā honti; "
360207,94,810,44,53,1,87,9,puratthimāya disāya dhataraṭṭho mahārājā pacchimābhimukho nisinno hoti deve purakkhatvā; 
360208,94,810,54,63,1,81,9,dakkhiṇāya disāya virūḷhako mahārājā uttarābhimukho nisinno hoti deve purakkhatvā; 
360209,94,810,64,74,1,84,9,pacchimāya disāya virūpakkho mahārājā puratthābhimukho nisinno hoti deve purakkhatvā; 
360210,94,810,75,84,1,81,9,uttarāya disāya vessavaṇo mahārājā dakkhiṇābhimukho nisinno hoti deve purakkhatvā. 
360211,94,810,85,117,1,209,27,"Yadā bhante, kevalakappā ca devā tāvatiṃsā sudhammāyaṃ sabhāyaṃ sannisinnā honti sannipatitā, mahatī ca dibbaparisā samantato nisinnā honti, cattāro ca mahārājāno catuddisā nisinnā honti, idaṃ nesaṃ hoti āsanasmiṃ; "
360212,94,810,118,123,1,31,5,atha pacchā amhākaṃ āsanaṃ hoti.
360213,94,811,2,25,1,125,18,"‘ ‘ Ye te, bhante, devā bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ caritvā adhunūpapannā tāvatiṃsakāyaṃ, te aññe deve atirocanti vaṇṇena ceva yasasā ca. "
360214,94,811,26,38,1,74,9,"Tena sudaṃ, bhante, devā tāvatiṃsā attamanā honti pamuditā pītisomanassajātā;"
360215,94,811,39,52,1,52,8,"‘ dibbā vata, bho, kāyā paripūrenti, hāyanti asurakāyā’ ti. "
360216,94,812,2,22,1,95,12,"295.‘‘ Atha kho, bhante, sakko devānamindo devānaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ sampasādaṃ viditvā imāhi gāthāhi anumodi–"
