360693,94,964,2,5,1,36,3,Mahāgovindasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ. 
360694,94,965,2,5,1,16,1,7. Mahāsamayasuttaṃ 
360695,94,966,2,28,1,156,17,331. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ mahāvane mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi; 
360696,94,966,29,39,1,96,10,dasahi ca lokadhātūhi devatā yebhuyyena sannipatitā honti bhagavantaṃ dassanāya bhikkhusaṅghañca. 
360697,94,966,40,57,1,57,6,Atha kho catunnaṃ suddhāvāsakāyikānaṃ devatānaṃ[ devānaṃ( sī. syā. pī.)] etadahosi–
360698,94,966,58,74,1,138,14,‘‘ ayaṃ kho bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ mahāvane mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi; 
