361438,94,1413,2,22,1,144,17,"‘ ‘ Iti ajjhattaṃ vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati, bahiddhā vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati, ajjhattabahiddhā vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati. "
361439,94,1413,23,60,1,265,31,"Samudayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati, vayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati, samudayavayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati‘ atthi dhammā’ ti vā panassa sati paccupaṭṭhitā hoti yāvadeva ñāṇamattāya paṭissatimattāya anissito ca viharati, na ca kiñci loke upādiyati. "
361440,94,1413,61,72,1,80,9,"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati sattasu bojjhaṅgesu. "
361441,94,1414,2,14,1,25,2,"Bojjhaṅgapabbaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.[ bojjhaṅgapabbaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ, paṭhamabhāṇavāraṃ( syā.)] "
361442,94,1415,2,3,1,27,2,Dhammānupassanā saccapabbaṃ 
361443,94,1416,2,19,1,82,9,"386.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati catūsu ariyasaccesu. "
361444,94,1416,20,31,1,83,9,"Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati catūsu ariyasaccesu? "
361445,94,1416,32,69,1,204,24,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
361446,94,1417,2,4,1,25,2,Paṭhamabhāṇavāro niṭṭhito. 
361447,94,1418,2,2,1,18,1,Dukkhasaccaniddeso 
361448,94,1419,2,17,1,39,4,"387.‘‘ Katamañca , bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ? "
361449,94,1419,18,72,1,217,22,"Jātipi dukkhā, jarāpi dukkhā, maraṇampi dukkhaṃ, sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsāpi dukkhā, appiyehi sampayogopi dukkho, piyehi vippayogopi dukkho[ appiyehi… pe… vippayogo dukkhotipāṭho ceva taṃniddeso ca katthaci na dissati, aṭṭhakathāyaṃpi taṃsaṃvaṇṇanā natthi], yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ, saṅkhittena pañcupādānakkhandhā[ pañcupādānakkhandhāpi( ka.)] dukkhā. "
361450,94,1420,2,14,1,24,4,"388.‘‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, jāti? "
361451,94,1420,15,37,1,151,19,"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhi tamhi sattanikāye jāti sañjāti okkanti abhinibbatti khandhānaṃ pātubhāvo āyatanānaṃ paṭilābho, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, jāti. "
361452,94,1421,2,15,1,24,4,"389.‘‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, jarā? "
361453,94,1421,16,39,1,155,20,"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhi tamhi sattanikāye jarā jīraṇatā khaṇḍiccaṃ pāliccaṃ valittacatā āyuno saṃhāni indriyānaṃ paripāko, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, jarā. "
361454,94,1422,2,13,1,27,3,"390.‘‘ Katamañca, bhikkhave, maraṇaṃ? "
361455,94,1422,14,44,1,199,23,"Yaṃ[ aṭṭhakathā oloketabbā] tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhā tamhā sattanikāyā cuti cavanatā bhedo antaradhānaṃ maccu maraṇaṃ kālakiriyā khandhānaṃ bhedo kaḷevarassa nikkhepo jīvitindriyassupacchedo, idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, maraṇaṃ. "
361456,94,1423,2,14,1,24,4,"391.‘‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, soko? "
361457,94,1423,15,39,1,176,18,"Yo kho, bhikkhave, aññataraññatarena byasanena samannāgatassa aññataraññatarena dukkhadhammena phuṭṭhassa soko socanā socitattaṃ antosoko antoparisoko, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, soko. "
361458,94,1424,2,14,1,28,4,"392.‘‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, paridevo? "
361459,94,1424,15,38,1,196,19,"Yo kho, bhikkhave, aññataraññatarena byasanena samannāgatassa aññataraññatarena dukkhadhammena phuṭṭhassa ādevo paridevo ādevanā paridevanā ādevitattaṃ paridevitattaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave paridevo. "
361460,94,1425,2,14,1,27,3,"393.‘‘ Katamañca , bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ? "
361461,94,1425,15,35,1,121,15,"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, kāyikaṃ dukkhaṃ kāyikaṃ asātaṃ kāyasamphassajaṃ dukkhaṃ asātaṃ vedayitaṃ, idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ. "
361462,94,1426,2,14,1,30,3,"394.‘‘ Katamañca , bhikkhave, domanassaṃ? "
361463,94,1426,15,35,1,128,15,"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ cetasikaṃ asātaṃ manosamphassajaṃ dukkhaṃ asātaṃ vedayitaṃ, idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, domanassaṃ. "
361464,94,1427,2,14,1,27,4,"395.‘‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, upāyāso? "
361465,94,1427,15,37,1,174,17,"Yo kho, bhikkhave, aññataraññatarena byasanena samannāgatassa aññataraññatarena dukkhadhammena phuṭṭhassa āyāso upāyāso āyāsitattaṃ upāyāsitattaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, upāyāso. "
361466,94,1428,2,17,1,45,6,"396.‘‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, appiyehi sampayogo dukkho? "
361467,94,1428,18,58,1,261,35,"Idha yassa te honti aniṭṭhā akantā amanāpā rūpā saddā gandhā rasā phoṭṭhabbā dhammā, ye vā panassa te honti anatthakāmā ahitakāmā aphāsukakāmā ayogakkhemakāmā, yā tehi saddhiṃ saṅgati samāgamo samodhānaṃ missībhāvo, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, appiyehi sampayogo dukkho. "
361468,94,1429,2,16,1,43,6,"397.‘‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, piyehi vippayogo dukkho? "
361469,94,1429,17,71,1,325,49,"Idha yassa te honti iṭṭhā kantā manāpā rūpā saddā gandhā rasā phoṭṭhabbā dhammā, ye vā panassa te honti atthakāmā hitakāmā phāsukakāmā yogakkhemakāmā mātā vā pitā vā bhātā vā bhaginī vā mittā vā amaccā vā ñātisālohitā vā, yā tehi saddhiṃ asaṅgati asamāgamo asamodhānaṃ amissībhāvo, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, piyehi vippayogo dukkho. "
361470,94,1430,2,19,1,55,7,"398.‘‘ Katamañca , bhikkhave, yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ? "
361471,94,1430,20,28,1,53,6,"Jātidhammānaṃ, bhikkhave, sattānaṃ evaṃ icchā uppajjati–"
361472,94,1430,29,45,1,68,13,"‘ aho vata mayaṃ na jātidhammā assāma, na ca vata no jāti āgaccheyyā’ ti. "
361473,94,1430,46,58,1,75,11,"Na kho panetaṃ icchāya pattabbaṃ, idampi yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ. "
361474,94,1430,59,67,1,53,6,"Jarādhammānaṃ, bhikkhave, sattānaṃ evaṃ icchā uppajjati–"
361475,94,1430,68,84,1,68,13,"‘ aho vata mayaṃ na jarādhammā assāma, na ca vata no jarā āgaccheyyā’ ti. "
361476,94,1430,85,97,1,75,11,"Na kho panetaṃ icchāya pattabbaṃ, idampi yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ. "
361477,94,1430,98,122,1,128,19,"Byādhidhammānaṃ, bhikkhave, sattānaṃ evaṃ icchā uppajjati‘ aho vata mayaṃ na byādhidhammā assāma, na ca vata no byādhi āgaccheyyā’ ti. "
361478,94,1430,123,135,1,75,11,"Na kho panetaṃ icchāya pattabbaṃ, idampi yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ. "
361479,94,1430,136,160,1,129,19,"Maraṇadhammānaṃ, bhikkhave, sattānaṃ evaṃ icchā uppajjati‘ aho vata mayaṃ na maraṇadhammā assāma, na ca vata no maraṇaṃ āgaccheyyā’ ti. "
361480,94,1430,161,173,1,75,11,"Na kho panetaṃ icchāya pattabbaṃ, idampi yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ. "
361481,94,1430,174,199,1,216,19,"Sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammānaṃ, bhikkhave, sattānaṃ evaṃ icchā uppajjati‘ aho vata mayaṃ na sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā assāma, na ca vata no sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā āgaccheyyun’ ti. "
361482,94,1430,200,212,1,75,11,"Na kho panetaṃ icchāya pattabbaṃ, idampi yampicchaṃ na labhati tampi dukkhaṃ. "
361483,94,1431,2,17,1,58,6,"399.‘‘ Katame ca, bhikkhave, saṅkhittena pañcupādānakkhandhā dukkhā? "
361484,94,1431,18,29,1,116,6,"Seyyathidaṃ– rūpupādānakkhandho, vedanupādānakkhandho, saññupādānakkhandho, saṅkhārupādānakkhandho, viññāṇupādānakkhandho. "
361485,94,1431,30,38,1,61,6,"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, saṅkhittena pañcupādānakkhandhā dukkhā. "
361486,94,1431,39,46,1,42,5,"Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ. "
361487,94,1432,2,2,1,20,1,Samudayasaccaniddeso 
361488,94,1433,2,22,1,47,4,"400.‘‘ Katamañca , bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ[ dukkhasamudayo( syā.)] ariyasaccaṃ? "
361489,94,1433,23,54,1,109,9,"Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobbhavikā[ ponobhavikā( sī. pī.)] nandīrāgasahagatā[ nandirāgasahagatā( sī. syā. pī.)] tatratatrābhinandinī, seyyathidaṃ– kāmataṇhā bhavataṇhā vibhavataṇhā."
361490,94,1434,2,18,1,85,12,"‘ ‘ Sā kho panesā, bhikkhave, taṇhā kattha uppajjamānā uppajjati, kattha nivisamānā nivisati? "
361491,94,1434,19,33,1,90,11,"Yaṃ loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati."
361492,94,1435,2,8,1,30,5,‘ ‘ Kiñca loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ? 
361493,94,1435,9,22,1,93,11,"Cakkhu loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati. "
361494,94,1435,23,50,1,138,20,"Sotaṃ loke… pe… ghānaṃ loke… jivhā loke… kāyo loke… mano loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati."
361495,94,1436,2,32,1,152,22,"‘ ‘ Rūpā loke… saddā loke… gandhā loke… rasā loke… phoṭṭhabbā loke… dhammā loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati."
361496,94,1437,2,32,1,193,22,"‘ ‘ Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ loke… sotaviññāṇaṃ loke… ghānaviññāṇaṃ loke… jivhāviññāṇaṃ loke… kāyaviññāṇaṃ loke… manoviññāṇaṃ loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati."
361497,94,1438,2,34,1,199,22,"‘ ‘ Cakkhusamphasso loke… sotasamphasso loke… ghānasamphasso loke… jivhāsamphasso loke… kāyasamphasso loke… manosamphasso loke piyarūpaṃ sātarūpaṃ, etthesā taṇhā uppajjamānā uppajjati, ettha nivisamānā nivisati."
