361507,94,1446,23,32,1,71,8,Yo tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodho cāgo paṭinissaggo mutti anālayo.
361508,94,1447,2,19,1,87,12,"‘ ‘ Sā kho panesā, bhikkhave, taṇhā kattha pahīyamānā pahīyati, kattha nirujjhamānā nirujjhati? "
