361523,94,1458,2,2,1,17,1,Maggasaccaniddeso 
361524,94,1459,2,15,1,60,5,"402.‘‘ Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ? "
361525,94,1459,16,30,1,138,13,Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo seyyathidaṃ– sammādiṭṭhi sammāsaṅkappo sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo sammāvāyāmo sammāsati sammāsamādhi.
361526,94,1460,2,10,1,31,5,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sammādiṭṭhi? "
361527,94,1460,11,36,1,145,16,"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dukkhe ñāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye ñāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe ñāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammādiṭṭhi."
361528,94,1461,2,11,1,33,5,"‘ ‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sammāsaṅkappo? "
361529,94,1461,12,21,1,88,7,"Nekkhammasaṅkappo abyāpādasaṅkappo avihiṃsāsaṅkappo, ayaṃ vuccati bhikkhave, sammāsaṅkappo."
361530,94,1462,2,11,1,29,5,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sammāvācā? "
361531,94,1462,12,36,1,124,14,"Musāvādā veramaṇī[ veramaṇi( ka.)] pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇī pharusāya vācāya veramaṇī samphappalāpā veramaṇī, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammāvācā."
361532,94,1463,2,10,1,33,5,"‘ ‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sammākammanto? "
361533,94,1463,11,24,1,102,10,"Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī adinnādānā veramaṇī kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇī, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammākammanto."
361534,94,1464,2,10,1,30,5,"‘ ‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sammāājīvo? "
361535,94,1464,11,28,1,109,12,"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako micchāājīvaṃ pahāya sammāājīvena jīvitaṃ kappeti, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammāājīvo."
361536,94,1465,2,10,1,31,5,"‘ ‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sammāvāyāmo? "
361537,94,1465,11,30,1,145,16,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati; "
361538,94,1465,31,44,1,118,13,uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati; 
361539,94,1465,45,57,1,109,12,anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati; 
361540,94,1465,58,76,1,162,17,uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati. 
361541,94,1465,77,83,1,34,4,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammāvāyāmo."
361542,94,1466,2,10,1,29,5,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, sammāsati? "
361543,94,1466,11,25,1,103,12,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
361544,94,1466,26,35,1,86,9,vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; 
361545,94,1466,36,45,1,82,9,citte cittānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; 
361546,94,1466,46,55,1,86,9,dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. 
361547,94,1466,56,62,1,32,4,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sammāsati."
361548,94,1467,2,10,1,32,5,"‘ ‘ Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sammāsamādhi? "
361549,94,1467,11,29,1,145,16,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
361550,94,1467,30,46,1,144,14,Vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
361551,94,1467,47,76,1,179,24,"Pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati, sato ca sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti‘ upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
361552,94,1467,77,92,1,156,15,Sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
361553,94,1467,93,100,1,35,4,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave , sammāsamādhi. "
361554,94,1467,101,109,1,63,6,"Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
361555,94,1468,2,27,1,144,16,"403.‘‘ Iti ajjhattaṃ vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati, bahiddhā vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati, ajjhattabahiddhā vā dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati. "
361556,94,1468,28,42,1,128,12,"Samudayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati, vayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati, samudayavayadhammānupassī vā dhammesu viharati."
361557,94,1468,43,65,1,136,19,"‘ Atthi dhammā’ ti vā panassa sati paccupaṭṭhitā hoti yāvadeva ñāṇamattāya paṭissatimattāya anissito ca viharati, na ca kiñci loke upādiyati. "
361558,94,1468,66,77,1,80,9,"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati catūsu ariyasaccesu. "
361559,94,1469,2,4,1,21,2,Saccapabbaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ. 
361560,94,1470,2,4,1,24,2,Dhammānupassanā niṭṭhitā. 
361561,94,1471,2,30,1,145,19,"404.‘‘ Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne evaṃ bhāveyya sattavassāni, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme aññā; "
361562,94,1471,31,36,1,27,4,sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā.
361563,94,1472,2,9,1,32,4,"‘ ‘ Tiṭṭhantu, bhikkhave, sattavassāni. "
361564,94,1472,10,47,1,172,26,"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne evaṃ bhāveyya cha vassāni… pe… pañca vassāni… cattāri vassāni… tīṇi vassāni… dve vassāni… ekaṃ vassaṃ… tiṭṭhatu, bhikkhave, ekaṃ vassaṃ. "
361565,94,1472,48,70,1,144,19,"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne evaṃ bhāveyya sattamāsāni, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme aññā; "
361566,94,1472,71,75,1,27,4,sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā.
361567,94,1473,2,11,1,32,5,"‘ ‘ Tiṭṭhantu , bhikkhave, satta māsāni. "
361568,94,1473,12,52,1,175,26,"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne evaṃ bhāveyya cha māsāni… pe… pañca māsāni… cattāri māsāni… tīṇi māsāni … dve māsāni… ekaṃ māsaṃ… aḍḍhamāsaṃ… tiṭṭhatu, bhikkhave, aḍḍhamāso. "
361569,94,1473,53,75,1,141,19,"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne evaṃ bhāveyya sattāhaṃ, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme aññā; "
361570,94,1473,76,80,1,29,4,sati vā upādisese anāgāmitāti. 
361571,94,1474,2,27,1,186,17,"405.‘‘ Ekāyano ayaṃ, bhikkhave, maggo sattānaṃ visuddhiyā sokaparidevānaṃ samatikkamāya dukkhadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamāya ñāyassa adhigamāya nibbānassa sacchikiriyāya yadidaṃ cattāro satipaṭṭhānāti. "
361572,94,1474,28,39,1,45,8,"Iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttan’’ ti. "
361573,94,1474,40,42,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
