361576,94,1476,2,5,1,12,1,10. Pāyāsisuttaṃ 
361577,94,1477,2,32,1,178,21,406. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā kumārakassapo kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi yena setabyā nāma kosalānaṃ nagaraṃ tadavasari. 
361578,94,1477,33,49,1,82,9,Tatra sudaṃ āyasmā kumārakassapo setabyāyaṃ viharati uttarena setabyaṃ siṃsapāvane[ sīsapāvane( syā.)]. 
361579,94,1477,50,68,1,166,18,Tena kho pana samayena pāyāsi rājañño setabyaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ. 
361580,94,1478,2,2,1,19,1,Pāyāsirājaññavatthu 
361581,94,1479,2,17,1,86,11,407. Tena kho pana samayena pāyāsissa rājaññassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ hoti–
361582,94,1479,18,47,1,95,13,"‘‘ itipi natthi paro loko, natthi sattā opapātikā, natthi sukatadukkaṭānaṃ [ sukaṭakkaṭānaṃ( sī. pī.)] kammānaṃ phalaṃ vipāko’’ ti. "
361583,94,1479,48,52,1,40,4,Assosuṃ kho setabyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
361584,94,1479,53,77,1,210,22,‘‘ samaṇo khalu bho kumārakassapo samaṇassa gotamassa sāvako kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi setabyaṃ anuppatto setabyāyaṃ viharati uttarena setabyaṃ siṃsapāvane. 
361585,94,1479,78,87,1,72,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ kumārakassapaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
361586,94,1479,88,108,1,81,10,‘ paṇḍito byatto medhāvī bahussuto cittakathī kalyāṇapaṭibhāno vuddho[ buddho( syā. ka.)] ceva arahā ca. 
361587,94,1479,109,120,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’’ ti. 
361588,94,1479,121,146,1,124,12,"Atha kho setabyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā setabyāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā uttarenamukhā gacchanti yena siṃsapāvanaṃ[ yena siṃsapāvanaṃ, tenupasaṅkamanti( sī. pī.)]. "
361589,94,1480,2,16,1,73,10,408. Tena kho pana samayena pāyāsi rājañño uparipāsāde divāseyyaṃ upagato hoti. 
361590,94,1480,17,48,1,164,17,"Addasā kho pāyāsi rājañño setabyake brāhmaṇagahapatike setabyāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūte uttarenamukhe gacchante yena siṃsapāvanaṃ[ yena siṃsapāvanaṃ, tenupasaṅkamante( sī. pī.)], disvā khattaṃ āmantesi –"
361591,94,1480,49,82,1,140,16,"‘‘ kiṃ nu kho, bho khatte, setabyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā setabyāya nikkhamitvā saṅghasaṅghī gaṇībhūtā uttarenamukhā gacchanti yena siṃsapāvanan’’ ti[ ettha pana sabbatthapi evameva dissati, natthi pāṭhantaraṃ]?"
361592,94,1481,2,31,1,214,24,"‘ ‘ Atthi kho, bho, samaṇo kumārakassapo, samaṇassa gotamassa sāvako kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi setabyaṃ anuppatto setabyāyaṃ viharati uttarena setabyaṃ siṃsapāvane. "
361593,94,1481,32,41,1,72,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ kumārakassapaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
361594,94,1481,42,65,1,84,11,‘ paṇḍito byatto medhāvī bahussuto cittakathī kalyāṇapaṭibhāno vuddho ceva arahā cā’ ti[ arahā ca( syā. ka.)]. 
361595,94,1481,66,90,1,58,6,"Tamete[ tamenaṃ te( sī. ka.), tamenaṃ( pī.)] bhavantaṃ kumārakassapaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamantī’’ ti."
361596,94,1481,91,103,1,66,8,"‘‘ Tena hi, bho khatte, yena setabyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkama; "
361597,94,1481,104,109,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā setabyake brāhmaṇagahapatike evaṃ vadehi–
361598,94,1481,110,131,1,118,14,"‘ pāyāsi, bho, rājañño evamāha – āgamentu kira bhavanto, pāyāsipi rājañño samaṇaṃ kumārakassapaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’ ti. "
361599,94,1481,132,140,1,77,8,Purā samaṇo kumārakassapo setabyake brāhmaṇagahapatike bāle abyatte saññāpeti–
361600,94,1481,141,158,1,92,13,"‘ itipi atthi paro loko, atthi sattā opapātikā, atthi sukatadukkaṭānaṃ kammānaṃ phalaṃ vipāko’ ti. "
361601,94,1481,159,180,1,103,15,"Natthi hi, bho khatte, paro loko, natthi sattā opapātikā, natthi sukatadukkaṭānaṃ kammānaṃ phalaṃ vipāko’’ ti."
361602,94,1481,181,198,1,105,13,‘‘ Evaṃ bho’’ ti kho so khattā pāyāsissa rājaññassa paṭissutvā yena setabyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tenupasaṅkami; 
361603,94,1481,199,203,1,52,4,upasaṅkamitvā setabyake brāhmaṇagahapatike etadavoca–
361604,94,1481,204,226,1,118,14,"‘‘ pāyāsi, bho, rājañño evamāha, āgamentu kira bhavanto, pāyāsipi rājañño samaṇaṃ kumārakassapaṃ dassanāya upasaṅkamissatī’’ ti. "
361605,94,1482,2,18,1,121,12,409. Atha kho pāyāsi rājañño setabyakehi brāhmaṇagahapatikehi parivuto yena siṃsapāvanaṃ yenāyasmā kumārakassapo tenupasaṅkami; 
361606,94,1482,19,33,1,113,11,"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā kumārakassapena saddhiṃ sammodi, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
