362334,95,18,160,189,1,81,10,"Yaṃ kho panetaṃ, sunakkhatta, maññasi acelaṃ korakkhattiyaṃ– sādhurūpo ayaṃ samaṇoti[ maññasi‘‘ acelo korakhattiyo sādhurūpo arahaṃ samaṇoti’’( syā.)]. "
362335,95,18,190,195,1,44,5,So sattamaṃ divasaṃ alasakena kālaṅkarissati. 
362336,95,18,196,232,1,77,9,"Kālaṅkato[ kālakato( sī. syā. pī.)] ca kālakañcikā[ kālakañjā( sī. pī.), kālakañjikā( syā.)] nāma asurā sabbanihīno asurakāyo, tatra upapajjissati. "
362337,95,18,233,238,1,52,5,Kālaṅkatañca naṃ bīraṇatthambake susāne chaḍḍessanti. 
362338,95,18,239,265,1,121,13,"Ākaṅkhamāno ca tvaṃ, sunakkhatta, acelaṃ korakkhattiyaṃ upasaṅkamitvā puccheyyāsi– jānāsi, āvuso korakkhattiya[ acela korakhattiya( ka.)], attano gatinti? "
362339,95,18,266,286,1,116,15,"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, sunakkhatta, vijjati yaṃ te acelo korakkhattiyo byākarissati– jānāmi, āvuso sunakkhatta, attano gatiṃ; "
