362346,95,19,60,75,1,99,12,"Yena tvaṃ, āvuso korakkhattiya, mattaṃ mattañca bhattaṃ bhuñjeyyāsi, mattaṃ mattañca pānīyaṃ piveyyāsi. "
362347,95,19,76,84,1,48,7,Yathā samaṇassa gotamassa micchā assa vacanan’ ti. 
362348,95,20,2,23,1,117,12,"8.‘‘ Atha kho, bhaggava, sunakkhatto licchaviputto ekadvīhikāya sattarattindivāni gaṇesi, yathā taṃ tathāgatassa asaddahamāno. "
