362547,95,53,2,28,1,120,18,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ vutte, bhaggava, acelo pāthikaputto‘ āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvuso’ ti vatvā tattheva saṃsappati, na sakkoti āsanāpi vuṭṭhātuṃ. "
