362549,95,53,40,63,1,107,18,"‘ kiṃ su nāma te, āvuso pāthikaputta, pāvaḷā su nāma te pīṭhakasmiṃ allīnā, pīṭhakaṃ su nāma te pāvaḷāsu allīnaṃ ? "
362550,95,53,64,80,1,83,12,"Āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvusoti vatvā tattheva saṃsappasi, na sakkosi āsanāpi vuṭṭhātun’ ti . "
362551,95,53,81,105,1,130,18,"Evampi kho, bhaggava, vuccamāno acelo pāthikaputto‘ āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvuso’ ti vatvā tattheva saṃsappati, na sakkoti āsanāpi vuṭṭhātuṃ. "
362552,95,54,2,16,1,45,6,"25.‘‘ Yadā kho so, bhaggava, licchavimahāmatto aññāsi–"
362553,95,54,17,38,1,121,16,"‘ parābhūtarūpo ayaṃ acelo pāthikaputto āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvusoti vatvā tattheva saṃsappati, na sakkoti āsanāpi vuṭṭhātun’ ti. "
362554,95,54,39,44,1,36,5,Atha taṃ parisaṃ āgantvā evamārocesi–
362555,95,54,45,83,1,120,16,"‘ parābhūtarūpo, bho[ parābhūtarūpo( sī. pī.), parābhūtarūpo ayaṃ( syā.)], acelo pāthikaputto āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvusoti vatvā tattheva saṃsappati, na sakkoti āsanāpi vuṭṭhātun’ ti. "
362556,95,54,84,94,1,47,7,"Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhaggava, taṃ parisaṃ etadavocaṃ–"
362557,95,54,95,115,1,133,17,"‘ abhabbo kho, āvuso, acelo pāthikaputto taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā mama sammukhībhāvaṃ āgantuṃ. "
362558,95,54,116,137,1,165,19,"Sacepissa evamassa– ahaṃ taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā samaṇassa gotamassa sammukhībhāvaṃ gaccheyyanti, muddhāpi tassa vipateyya. "
362559,95,54,138,181,1,148,16,"Sace pāyasmantānaṃ licchavīnaṃ evamassa– mayaṃ acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ varattāhi[ yāhi varattāhi( syā. ka.)] bandhitvā goyugehi āviñcheyyāmāti[ āviñjeyyāmāti( syā.), āvijjheyyāmāti( sī. pī.)], tā varattā chijjeyyuṃ pāthikaputto vā. "
362560,95,54,182,198,1,128,16,Abhabbo pana acelo pāthikaputto taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā mama sammukhībhāvaṃ āgantuṃ. 
362561,95,54,199,223,1,168,20,"Sacepissa evamassa– ahaṃ taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā samaṇassa gotamassa sammukhībhāvaṃ gaccheyyanti, muddhāpi tassa vipateyyā’ ti. "
362562,95,55,2,19,1,77,9,"26.‘‘ Atha kho, bhaggava, jāliyo dārupattikantevāsī uṭṭhāyāsanā taṃ parisaṃ etadavoca–"
362563,95,55,20,32,1,51,8,"‘ tena hi, bho, muhuttaṃ tāva āgametha, yāvāhaṃ gacchāmi; "
362564,95,55,33,45,1,74,10,appeva nāma ahampi sakkuṇeyyaṃ acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ imaṃ parisaṃ ānetun’’ ti.
362565,95,56,2,19,1,114,12,"‘ ‘ Atha kho, bhaggava, jāliyo dārupattikantevāsī yena tindukakhāṇuparibbājakārāmo, yena acelo pāthikaputto tenupasaṅkami. "
362566,95,56,20,25,1,44,4,Upasaṅkamitvā acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ etadavoca–
362567,95,56,26,33,1,47,5,"‘ abhikkamāvuso pāthikaputta, abhikkantaṃ te seyyo. "
362568,95,56,34,47,1,135,12,"Abhikkantā abhiññātā abhiññātā licchavī, abhikkantā abhiññātā abhiññātā ca brāhmaṇamahāsālā gahapatinecayikā nānātitthiyā samaṇabrāhmaṇā. "
362569,95,56,48,54,1,50,6,Samaṇopi gotamo āyasmato ārāme divāvihāraṃ nisinno. 
362570,95,56,55,77,1,130,17,"Bhāsitā kho pana te esā, āvuso pāthikaputta, vesāliyaṃ parisati vācā– samaṇopi gotamo ñāṇavādo… pe… taddiguṇaṃ taddiguṇāhaṃ karissāmīti. "
362571,95,56,78,85,1,51,5,"Abhikkamasseva, kho āvuso pāthikaputta, upaḍḍhapathaṃ. "
362572,95,56,86,95,1,74,8,Sabbapaṭhamaṃyeva āgantvā samaṇo gotamo āyasmato ārāme divāvihāraṃ nisinno. 
362573,95,56,96,123,1,193,24,"Bhāsitā kho panesā, āvuso pāthikaputta, samaṇena gotamena parisati vācā– abhabbo acelo pāthikaputto taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā mama sammukhībhāvaṃ āgantuṃ. "
362574,95,56,124,145,1,165,19,"Sacepissa evamassa– ahaṃ taṃ vācaṃ appahāya taṃ cittaṃ appahāya taṃ diṭṭhiṃ appaṭinissajjitvā samaṇassa gotamassa sammukhībhāvaṃ gaccheyyanti, muddhāpi tassa vipateyya. "
362575,95,56,146,158,1,110,11,Sace pāyasmantānaṃ licchavīnaṃ evamassa– mayaṃ acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ varattāhi bandhitvā goyugehi āviñcheyyāmāti. 
362576,95,56,159,164,1,37,5,Tā varattā chijjeyyuṃ pāthikaputto vā. 
