362585,95,58,2,16,1,50,6,"27.‘‘ Yadā kho, bhaggava, jāliyo dārupattikantevāsī aññāsi–"
362586,95,58,17,42,1,140,19,"‘ parābhūtarūpo ayaṃ acelo pāthikaputto‘ āyāmi āvuso, āyāmi āvusoti vatvā tattheva saṃsappati, na sakkoti āsanāpi vuṭṭhātun’ ti, atha naṃ etadavoca–"
362587,95,59,2,18,1,115,13,"‘ Bhūtapubbaṃ, āvuso pāthikaputta, sīhassa migarañño etadahosi– yaṃnūnāhaṃ aññataraṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ nissāya āsayaṃ kappeyyaṃ. "
362588,95,59,19,46,1,239,23,"Tatrāsayaṃ kappetvā sāyanhasamayaṃ āsayā nikkhameyyaṃ, āsayā nikkhamitvā vijambheyyaṃ, vijambhitvā samantā catuddisā anuvilokeyyaṃ, samantā catuddisā anuviloketvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadeyyaṃ, tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ naditvā gocarāya pakkameyyaṃ. "
362589,95,59,47,69,1,100,12,So varaṃ varaṃ migasaṃghe[ migasaṃghaṃ( syā. ka.)] vadhitvā mudumaṃsāni mudumaṃsāni bhakkhayitvā tameva āsayaṃ ajjhupeyyan’ ti.
362590,95,60,2,17,1,75,12,"‘ Atha kho, āvuso, so sīho migarājā aññataraṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ nissāya āsayaṃ kappesi. "
362591,95,60,18,46,1,221,23,"Tatrāsayaṃ kappetvā sāyanhasamayaṃ āsayā nikkhami, āsayā nikkhamitvā vijambhi, vijambhitvā samantā catuddisā anuvilokesi, samantā catuddisā anuviloketvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadi, tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ naditvā gocarāya pakkāmi. "
362592,95,60,47,58,1,95,11,So varaṃ varaṃ migasaṅghe vadhitvā mudumaṃsāni mudumaṃsāni bhakkhayitvā tameva āsayaṃ ajjhupesi. 
362593,95,61,2,33,1,98,12,"28.‘ Tasseva kho, āvuso pāthikaputta, sīhassa migarañño vighāsasaṃvaḍḍho jarasiṅgālo[ jarasigālo( sī. syā. pī.)] ditto ceva balavā ca. "
362594,95,61,34,49,1,71,11,"Atha kho, āvuso, tassa jarasiṅgālassa etadahosi– ko cāhaṃ, ko sīho migarājā. "
362595,95,61,50,56,1,58,6,Yaṃnūnāhampi aññataraṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ nissāya āsayaṃ kappeyyaṃ. 
362596,95,61,57,85,1,239,23,"Tatrāsayaṃ kappetvā sāyanhasamayaṃ āsayā nikkhameyyaṃ, āsayā nikkhamitvā vijambheyyaṃ, vijambhitvā samantā catuddisā anuvilokeyyaṃ, samantā catuddisā anuviloketvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadeyyaṃ, tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ naditvā gocarāya pakkameyyaṃ. "
362597,95,61,86,99,1,100,12,So varaṃ varaṃ migasaṅghe vadhitvā mudumaṃsāni mudumaṃsāni bhakkhayitvā tameva āsayaṃ ajjhupeyyan’ ti.
362598,95,62,2,15,1,73,11,"‘ Atha kho so, āvuso, jarasiṅgālo aññataraṃ vanasaṇḍaṃ nissāya āsayaṃ kappesi. "
362599,95,62,16,63,1,264,29,"Tatrāsayaṃ kappetvā sāyanhasamayaṃ āsayā nikkhami, āsayā nikkhamitvā vijambhi, vijambhitvā samantā catuddisā anuvilokesi, samantā catuddisā anuviloketvā tikkhattuṃ sīhanādaṃ nadissāmīti siṅgālakaṃyeva anadi bheraṇḍakaṃyeva[ bhedaṇḍakaṃyeva( ka.)] anadi, ke ca chave siṅgāle, ke pana sīhanādeti[ sīhanāde(?)]."
362600,95,63,2,20,1,140,15,"‘ Evameva kho tvaṃ, āvuso pāthikaputta, sugatāpadānesu jīvamāno sugatātirittāni bhuñjamāno tathāgate arahante sammāsambuddhe āsādetabbaṃ maññasi. "
362601,95,63,21,34,1,84,11,"Ke ca chave pāthikaputte, kā ca tathāgatānaṃ arahantānaṃ sammāsambuddhānaṃ āsādanā’ ti. "
362602,95,64,2,24,1,112,14,"29.‘‘ Yato kho, bhaggava, jāliyo dārupattikantevāsī iminā opammena neva asakkhi acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ tamhā āsanā cāvetuṃ. "
362603,95,64,25,28,1,18,3,Atha naṃ etadavoca–
