362605,95,66,2,5,1,29,3,Amaññi kotthu migarājāhamasmi; 
362606,95,67,2,13,1,27,4,"Tatheva [ tameva( syā.)] so siṅgālakaṃ anadi, "
362607,95,68,2,11,1,39,8,Ke ca chave siṅgāle ke pana sīhanāde’ ti.
