362638,95,86,2,67,1,413,39,"34.‘‘ Atha khvāhaṃ, bhaggava, taṃ parisaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, taṃ parisaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassetvā samādapetvā samuttejetvā sampahaṃsetvā mahābandhanā mokkhaṃ karitvā caturāsītipāṇasahassāni mahāviduggā uddharitvā tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā sattatālaṃ vehāsaṃ abbhuggantvā aññaṃ sattatālampi acciṃ[ aggiṃ( syā.)] abhinimminitvā pajjalitvā dhūmāyitvā [ dhūpāyitvā( sī. pī.)] mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ paccuṭṭhāsiṃ. "
362639,95,87,2,17,1,65,7,"35.‘‘ Atha kho, bhaggava, sunakkhatto licchaviputto yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
362640,95,87,18,23,1,46,5,upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
362641,95,87,24,34,1,75,8,"Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhaggava, sunakkhattaṃ licchaviputtaṃ etadavocaṃ–"
362642,95,87,35,57,1,115,17,"‘ taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sunakkhatta, yatheva te ahaṃ acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ ārabbha byākāsiṃ, tatheva taṃ vipākaṃ aññathā vā’ ti?"
362643,95,87,58,78,1,96,14,"‘ Yatheva me, bhante, bhagavā acelaṃ pāthikaputtaṃ ārabbha byākāsi, tatheva taṃ vipākaṃ, no aññathā’ ti."
362644,95,88,2,23,1,107,16,"‘ Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, sunakkhatta, yadi evaṃ sante kataṃ vā hoti uttarimanussadhammā iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ, akataṃ vā’ ti?"
362645,95,88,24,41,1,88,12,"‘ Addhā kho, bhante, evaṃ sante kataṃ hoti uttarimanussadhammā iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ, no akatan’ ti."
362646,95,88,42,69,1,164,19,"‘ Evampi kho maṃ tvaṃ, moghapurisa, uttarimanussadhammā iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karontaṃ evaṃ vadesi– na hi pana me, bhante, bhagavā uttarimanussadhammā iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ karotīti. "
362647,95,88,70,80,1,47,7,"Passa, moghapurisa, yāvañca te idaṃ aparaddhaṃ’ ti."
362648,95,89,2,21,1,118,15,"‘ ‘ Evampi kho, bhaggava, sunakkhatto licchaviputto mayā vuccamāno apakkameva imasmā dhammavinayā, yathā taṃ āpāyiko nerayiko. "
362649,95,90,2,2,1,20,1,Aggaññapaññattikathā 
362650,95,91,2,13,1,31,3,"36.‘‘ Aggaññañcāhaṃ, bhaggava, pajānāmi. "
362651,95,91,14,61,1,160,21,"Tañca pajānāmi[‘‘ tañcapajānāmī’’ ti idaṃ syāpotthakenatthi], tato ca uttaritaraṃ pajānāmi, tañca pajānaṃ[ pajānanaṃ( syā. ka.) aṭṭhakathāsaṃvaṇṇanā passitabbā] na parāmasāmi, aparāmasato ca me paccattaññeva nibbuti viditā, yadabhijānaṃ tathāgato no anayaṃ āpajjati . "
362652,95,92,2,19,1,90,9,"37.‘‘ Santi, bhaggava, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā issarakuttaṃ brahmakuttaṃ ācariyakaṃ aggaññaṃ paññapenti. "
