362657,95,92,61,82,1,96,10,‘ kathaṃvihitakaṃ pana[ kathaṃ vihitakaṃno pana( ka.)] tumhe āyasmanto issarakuttaṃ brahmakuttaṃ ācariyakaṃ aggaññaṃ paññapethā’ ti? 
