362679,95,97,48,52,1,31,4,mayaṃ panāmha pacchā upapannāti. 
362680,95,98,2,24,1,100,14,"40.‘ Tatrāvuso , yo so satto paṭhamaṃ upapanno, so dīghāyukataro ca hoti vaṇṇavantataro ca mahesakkhataro ca. "
