362766,95,113,102,116,1,89,11,"‘ yasmiṃ samaye subhaṃ vimokkhaṃ upasampajja viharati, subhantveva tasmiṃ samaye pajānātī’ ti."
362767,95,114,2,18,1,68,11,"‘ ‘ Te ca, bhante, viparītā, ye bhagavantaṃ viparītato dahanti bhikkhavo ca. "
362768,95,114,19,25,1,33,4,"Evaṃpasanno ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavati. "
