362777,95,117,1,4,1,16,1,2. Udumbarikasuttaṃ 
362778,95,118,2,2,1,25,1,Nigrodhaparibbājakavatthu 
362779,95,119,2,21,1,71,10,49. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. 
362780,95,119,22,36,1,151,14,Tena kho pana samayena nigrodho paribbājako udumbarikāya paribbājakārāme paṭivasati mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ tiṃsamattehi paribbājakasatehi. 
362781,95,119,37,58,1,79,10,Atha kho sandhāno gahapati divā divassa[ divādivasseva( sī. syā. pī.)] rājagahā nikkhami bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. 
362782,95,119,59,64,1,42,5,Atha kho sandhānassa gahapatissa etadahosi–
362783,95,119,65,71,1,31,4,‘‘ akālo kho bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. 
362784,95,119,72,74,1,19,2,Paṭisallīno bhagavā. 
362785,95,119,75,79,1,47,4,Manobhāvanīyānampi bhikkhūnaṃ asamayo dassanāya. 
362786,95,119,80,83,1,33,3,Paṭisallīnā manobhāvanīyā bhikkhū. 
362787,95,119,84,96,1,91,9,"Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena udumbarikāya paribbājakārāmo, yena nigrodho paribbājako tenupasaṅkameyyan’’ ti. "
362788,95,119,97,106,1,74,8,"Atha kho sandhāno gahapati yena udumbarikāya paribbājakārāmo, tenupasaṅkami. "
362789,95,120,2,22,1,166,16,50. Tena kho pana samayena nigrodho paribbājako mahatiyā paribbājakaparisāya saddhiṃ nisinno hoti unnādiniyā uccāsaddamahāsaddāya anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathentiyā. 
362790,95,120,23,56,1,375,30,Seyyathidaṃ– rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ senākathaṃ bhayakathaṃ yuddhakathaṃ annakathaṃ pānakathaṃ vatthakathaṃ sayanakathaṃ mālākathaṃ gandhakathaṃ ñātikathaṃ yānakathaṃ gāmakathaṃ nigamakathaṃ nagarakathaṃ janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ sūrakathaṃ visikhākathaṃ kumbhaṭṭhānakathaṃ pubbapetakathaṃ nānattakathaṃ lokakkhāyikaṃ samuddakkhāyikaṃ itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vā. 
362791,95,121,2,14,1,72,8,51. Addasā kho nigrodho paribbājako sandhānaṃ gahapatiṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
