362793,95,121,20,29,1,46,6,"‘‘ appasaddā bhonto hontu, mā bhonto saddamakattha. "
362794,95,121,30,37,1,59,7,Ayaṃ samaṇassa gotamassa sāvako āgacchati sandhāno gahapati. 
362795,95,121,38,54,1,118,15,"Yāvatā kho pana samaṇassa gotamassa sāvakā gihī odātavasanā rājagahe paṭivasanti, ayaṃ tesaṃ aññataro sandhāno gahapati. "
362796,95,121,55,65,1,75,7,"Appasaddakāmā kho panete āyasmanto appasaddavinītā , appasaddassa vaṇṇavādino. "
