362798,95,121,77,83,1,38,6,Evaṃ vutte te paribbājakā tuṇhī ahesuṃ. 
362799,95,122,2,20,1,121,13,"52. Atha kho sandhāno gahapati yena nigrodho paribbājako tenupasaṅkami, upasaṅkamitvā nigrodhena paribbājakena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
362800,95,122,21,27,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
