362836,95,126,102,129,1,164,19,"Evaṃ vutte, nigrodho paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca,‘‘ idha mayaṃ, bhante, addasāma bhagavantaṃ sumāgadhāya tīre moranivāpe abbhokāse caṅkamantaṃ, disvāna evaṃ avocumhā–"
