363108,95,193,45,47,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
363109,95,193,48,61,1,89,8,"‘‘ attadīpā, bhikkhave, viharatha attasaraṇā anaññasaraṇā, dhammadīpā dhammasaraṇā anaññasaraṇā. "
363110,95,193,62,76,1,110,11,"Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu attadīpo viharati attasaraṇo anaññasaraṇo, dhammadīpo dhammasaraṇo anaññasaraṇo? "
363111,95,193,77,91,1,103,12,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
363112,95,193,92,111,1,134,15,Vedanāsu vedanānupassī… pe… citte cittānupassī… pe… dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. 
363113,95,193,112,126,1,105,11,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu attadīpo viharati attasaraṇo anaññasaraṇo, dhammadīpo dhammasaraṇo anaññasaraṇo."
