363117,95,195,2,2,1,23,1,Daḷhanemicakkavattirājā 
363118,95,196,2,33,1,145,13,"81.‘‘ Bhūtapubbaṃ , bhikkhave, rājā daḷhanemi nāma ahosi cakkavattī[ cakkavatti( syā. pī.)] dhammiko dhammarājā cāturanto vijitāvī janapadatthāvariyappatto sattaratanasamannāgato. "
363119,95,196,34,50,1,154,13,Tassimāni satta ratanāni ahesuṃ seyyathidaṃ– cakkaratanaṃu hatthiratanaṃ assaratanaṃ maṇiratanaṃ itthiratanaṃ gahapatiratanaṃ pariṇāyakaratanameva sattamaṃ. 
363120,95,196,51,59,1,73,8,Parosahassaṃ kho panassa puttā ahesuṃ sūrā vīraṅgarūpā parasenappamaddanā. 
363121,95,196,60,79,1,82,9,So imaṃ pathaviṃ sāgarapariyantaṃ adaṇḍena asatthena dhammena[ dhammena samena( syā. ka.)] abhivijiya ajjhāvasi. 
363122,95,197,2,26,1,134,15,"82.‘‘ Atha kho, bhikkhave, rājā daḷhanemi bahunnaṃ vassānaṃ bahunnaṃ vassasatānaṃ bahunnaṃ vassasahassānaṃ accayena aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi–"
363123,95,197,27,46,1,97,14,"‘ yadā tvaṃ, ambho purisa, passeyyāsi dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ osakkitaṃ ṭhānā cutaṃ, atha me āroceyyāsī’ ti."
363124,95,197,47,62,1,66,10,"‘ Evaṃ, devā’ ti kho, bhikkhave, so puriso rañño daḷhanemissa paccassosi. "
363125,95,197,63,88,1,188,22,"Addasā kho, bhikkhave, so puriso bahunnaṃ vassānaṃ bahunnaṃ vassasatānaṃ bahunnaṃ vassasahassānaṃ accayena dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ osakkitaṃ ṭhānā cutaṃ, disvāna yena rājā daḷhanemi tenupasaṅkami; "
363126,95,197,89,93,1,42,4,upasaṅkamitvā rājānaṃ daḷhanemiṃ etadavoca–
363127,95,197,94,109,1,69,10,"‘ yagghe, deva, jāneyyāsi, dibbaṃ te cakkaratanaṃ osakkitaṃ ṭhānā cutan’ ti. "
363128,95,197,110,130,1,76,9,"Atha kho, bhikkhave, rājā daḷhanemi jeṭṭhaputtaṃ kumāraṃ āmantāpetvā[ āmantetvā( syā. ka.)] etadavoca–"
363129,95,197,131,143,1,61,9,"‘ dibbaṃ kira me, tāta kumāra, cakkaratanaṃ osakkitaṃ ṭhānā cutaṃ. "
363130,95,197,144,165,1,131,19,"Sutaṃ kho pana metaṃ– yassa rañño cakkavattissa dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ osakkati ṭhānā cavati, na dāni tena raññā ciraṃ jīvitabbaṃ hotīti. "
363131,95,197,166,180,1,70,12,"Bhuttā kho pana me mānusakā kāmā, samayo dāni me dibbe kāme pariyesituṃ. "
363132,95,197,181,191,1,62,8,"Ehi tvaṃ, tāta kumāra, imaṃ samuddapariyantaṃ pathaviṃ paṭipajja. "
363133,95,197,192,205,1,94,11,Ahaṃ pana kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajissāmī’ ti. 
363134,95,198,2,28,1,160,18,"83.‘‘ Atha kho, bhikkhave, rājā daḷhanemi jeṭṭhaputtaṃ kumāraṃ sādhukaṃ rajje samanusāsitvā kesamassuṃ ohāretvā kāsāyāni vatthāni acchādetvā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbaji. "
363135,95,198,29,39,1,77,8,"Sattāhapabbajite kho pana, bhikkhave, rājisimhi dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ antaradhāyi."
363136,95,199,2,28,1,82,11,"‘ ‘ Atha kho, bhikkhave, aññataro puriso yena rājā khattiyo muddhābhisitto[ muddhāvasitto( sī. syā. pī.) evamuparipi] tenupasaṅkami; "
363137,95,199,29,34,1,57,5,upasaṅkamitvā rājānaṃ khattiyaṃ muddhābhisittaṃ etadavoca–
363138,95,199,35,47,1,56,7,"‘ yagghe, deva, jāneyyāsi, dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ antarahitan’ ti. "
363139,95,199,48,64,1,123,13,"Atha kho, bhikkhave, rājā khattiyo muddhābhisitto dibbe cakkaratane antarahite anattamano ahosi, anattamanatañca paṭisaṃvedesi. "
363140,95,199,65,69,1,28,4,So yena rājisi tenupasaṅkami; 
363141,95,199,70,73,1,31,3,upasaṅkamitvā rājisiṃ etadavoca–
363142,95,199,74,86,1,56,7,"‘ yagghe, deva, jāneyyāsi, dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ antarahitan’ ti. "
363143,95,199,87,98,1,71,8,"Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhave, rājisi rājānaṃ khattiyaṃ muddhābhisittaṃ etadavoca–"
363144,95,199,99,127,1,147,20,"‘ mā kho tvaṃ, tāta, dibbe cakkaratane antarahite anattamano ahosi, mā anattamanatañca paṭisaṃvedesi, na hi te, tāta, dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ pettikaṃ dāyajjaṃ. "
363145,95,199,128,136,1,45,6,"Iṅgha tvaṃ, tāta, ariye cakkavattivatte vattāhi. "
363146,95,199,137,177,1,232,22,"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati, yaṃ te ariye cakkavattivatte vattamānassa tadahuposathe pannarase sīsaṃnhātassa[ sīsaṃ nahātassa( sī. pī.), sīsanhātassa( syā.)] uposathikassa uparipāsādavaragatassa dibbaṃ cakkaratanaṃ pātubhavissati sahassāraṃ sanemikaṃ sanābhikaṃ sabbākāraparipūran’ ti. "
363147,95,200,2,2,1,21,1,Cakkavattiariyavattaṃ 
363148,95,201,2,21,1,48,7,"84.‘‘‘ Katamaṃ pana taṃ, deva, ariyaṃ cakkavattivattan’ ti ?"
363149,95,201,22,76,1,329,31,"‘ Tena hi tvaṃ, tāta, dhammaṃyeva nissāya dhammaṃ sakkaronto dhammaṃ garuṃ karonto[ garukaronto( sī. syā. pī.)] dhammaṃ mānento dhammaṃ pūjento dhammaṃ apacāyamāno dhammaddhajo dhammaketu dhammādhipateyyo dhammikaṃ rakkhāvaraṇaguttiṃ saṃvidahassu antojanasmiṃ balakāyasmiṃ khattiyesu anuyantesu[ anuyuttesu( sī. pī.)] brāhmaṇagahapatikesu negamajānapadesu samaṇabrāhmaṇesu migapakkhīsu. "
363150,95,201,77,86,1,44,7,"Mā ca te, tāta, vijite adhammakāro pavattittha. "
363151,95,201,87,110,1,60,9,"Ye ca te, tāta, vijite adhanā assu, tesañca dhanamanuppadeyyāsi[ dhanamanuppadajjeyyāsi( sī. syā. pī.)]. "
363152,95,201,111,138,1,210,22,"Ye ca te, tāta, vijite samaṇabrāhmaṇā madappamādā paṭiviratā khantisoracce niviṭṭhā ekamattānaṃ damenti, ekamattānaṃ samenti, ekamattānaṃ parinibbāpenti, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripuccheyyāsi pariggaṇheyyāsi–"
363153,95,201,139,183,1,206,31,"‘‘ kiṃ, bhante, kusalaṃ, kiṃ akusalaṃ, kiṃ sāvajjaṃ, kiṃ anavajjaṃ, kiṃ sevitabbaṃ, kiṃ na sevitabbaṃ, kiṃ me karīyamānaṃ dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya assa, kiṃ vā pana me karīyamānaṃ dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāya assā’’ ti? "
363154,95,201,184,196,1,81,11,"Tesaṃ sutvā yaṃ akusalaṃ taṃ abhinivajjeyyāsi, yaṃ kusalaṃ taṃ samādāya vatteyyāsi. "
363155,95,201,197,207,1,44,7,"Idaṃ kho, tāta, taṃ ariyaṃ cakkavattivattan’ ti. "
