363355,95,241,30,34,1,31,4,Yaṃnūna mayaṃ kusalaṃ kareyyāma. 
363356,95,241,35,38,1,21,3,Kiṃ kusalaṃ kareyyāma? 
363357,95,241,39,51,1,80,10,"Yaṃnūna mayaṃ pāṇātipātā virameyyāma, idaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ samādāya vatteyyāmā’ ti. "
363358,95,241,52,61,1,68,8,"Te pāṇātipātā viramissanti, idaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ samādāya vattissanti. "
363359,95,241,62,72,1,79,8,"Te kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ samādānahetu āyunāpi vaḍḍhissanti, vaṇṇenapi vaḍḍhissanti . "
363360,95,241,73,83,1,113,10,Tesaṃ āyunāpi vaḍḍhamānānaṃ vaṇṇenapi vaḍḍhamānānaṃ dasavassāyukānaṃ manussānaṃ vīsativassāyukā puttā bhavissanti.
