363430,95,261,2,21,1,82,10,111. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde. 
363431,95,261,22,31,1,89,9,Tena kho pana samayena vāseṭṭhabhāradvājā bhikkhūsu parivasanti bhikkhubhāvaṃ ākaṅkhamānā. 
363432,95,261,32,50,1,106,11,Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito pāsādā orohitvā pāsādapacchāyāyaṃ[ pāsādacchāyāyaṃ( ka.)] abbhokāse caṅkamati. 
