363509,95,274,2,2,1,20,1,Rasapathavipātubhāvo 
363510,95,275,2,20,1,76,9,"120.‘‘ Ekodakībhūtaṃ kho pana, vāseṭṭha, tena samayena hoti andhakāro andhakāratimisā . "
