363512,95,275,52,73,1,105,13,"Atha kho tesaṃ, vāseṭṭha, sattānaṃ kadāci karahaci dīghassa addhuno accayena rasapathavī udakasmiṃ samatani[ samatāni( bahūsu)]; "
