364433,95,472,62,71,1,84,9,So imaṃ pathaviṃ sāgarapariyantaṃ adaṇḍena asatthena dhammena abhivijiya ajjhāvasati. 
364434,95,472,72,101,1,89,11,"Sace kho pana agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajati, arahaṃ hoti sammāsambuddho loke vivaṭṭacchado[ vivaṭacchado( syā. ka.), vivattacchado( sī. pī.)]. "
364435,95,473,2,26,1,134,14,"200.‘‘ Katamāni ca tāni, bhikkhave, dvattiṃsa mahāpurisassa mahāpurisalakkhaṇāni, yehi samannāgatassa mahāpurisassa dveva gatiyo bhavanti anaññā? "
