365043,95,903,85,96,1,40,7,"‘‘ Pitā maṃ, bhante, kālaṃ karonto evaṃ avaca–"
365044,95,903,97,105,1,25,4,"‘ disā, tāta, namasseyyāsī’ ti. "
365045,95,903,106,144,1,258,32,"So kho ahaṃ, bhante, pituvacanaṃ sakkaronto garuṃ karonto mānento pūjento kālasseva uṭṭhāya rājagahā nikkhamitvā allavattho allakeso pañjaliko puthudisā namassāmi– puratthimaṃ disaṃ dakkhiṇaṃ disaṃ pacchimaṃ disaṃ uttaraṃ disaṃ heṭṭhimaṃ disaṃ uparimaṃ disan’’ ti. "
365046,95,904,2,3,1,8,2,Cha disā 
365047,95,905,2,31,1,66,10,"244.‘‘ Na kho, gahapatiputta, ariyassa vinaye evaṃ cha disā[ chaddisā( sī. pī.)] namassitabbā’’ ti."
365048,95,905,32,54,1,62,9,"‘‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, bhante, ariyassa vinaye cha disā[ chaddisā( sī. pī.)] namassitabbā? "
365049,95,905,55,83,1,91,14,"Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā tathā dhammaṃ desetu, yathā ariyassa vinaye cha disā[ chaddisā( sī. pī.)] namassitabbā’’ ti."
365050,95,906,2,16,1,64,9,"‘ ‘ Tena hi, gahapatiputta suṇohi sādhukaṃ manasikarohi bhāsissāmī’’ ti."
365051,95,906,17,30,1,63,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho siṅgālako gahapatiputto bhagavato paccassosi. "
365052,95,906,31,33,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
365053,95,907,2,46,1,228,29,"‘ ‘ Yato kho, gahapatiputta, ariyasāvakassa cattāro kammakilesā pahīnā honti, catūhi ca ṭhānehi pāpakammaṃ na karoti, cha ca bhogānaṃ apāyamukhāni na sevati, so evaṃ cuddasa pāpakāpagato chaddisāpaṭicchādī[ paṭicchādī hoti( syā.)] ubholokavijayāya paṭipanno hoti. "
365054,95,907,47,55,1,45,8,Tassa ayañceva loko āraddho hoti paro ca loko. 
365055,95,907,56,65,1,61,9,So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. 
365056,95,908,2,2,1,18,1,Cattārokammakilesā 
365057,95,909,2,13,1,42,5,245.‘‘ Katamassa cattāro kammakilesā pahīnā honti? 
365058,95,909,14,29,1,114,10,"Pāṇātipāto kho, gahapatiputta, kammakileso, adinnādānaṃ kammakileso, kāmesumicchācāro kammakileso, musāvādo kammakileso. "
365059,95,909,30,38,1,42,6,Imassa cattāro kammakilesā pahīnā hontī’’ ti. 
365060,95,909,39,60,1,64,8,"Idamavoca bhagavā, idaṃ vatvāna[ idaṃ vatvā( sī. pī.) evamīdisesu ṭhānesu] sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā–"
365061,95,910,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Pāṇātipāto adinnādānaṃ, musāvādo ca vuccati; "
365062,95,911,2,9,1,44,4,"Paradāragamanañceva , nappasaṃsanti paṇḍitā’’ ti. "
365063,95,912,2,2,1,11,1,Catuṭṭhānaṃ 
365064,95,913,2,14,1,44,6,246.‘‘ Katamehi catūhi ṭhānehi pāpakammaṃ na karoti? 
365065,95,913,15,35,1,154,16,"Chandāgatiṃ gacchanto pāpakammaṃ karoti, dosāgatiṃ gacchanto pāpakammaṃ karoti, mohāgatiṃ gacchanto pāpakammaṃ karoti, bhayāgatiṃ gacchanto pāpakammaṃ karoti. "
365066,95,913,36,57,1,127,16,"Yato kho, gahapatiputta, ariyasāvako neva chandāgatiṃ gacchati, na dosāgatiṃ gacchati, na mohāgatiṃ gacchati, na bhayāgatiṃ gacchati; "
365067,95,913,58,67,1,44,7,imehi catūhi ṭhānehi pāpakammaṃ na karotī’’ ti. 
365068,95,913,68,77,1,64,8,"Idamavoca bhagavā, idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā–"
