365072,95,917,2,27,1,43,6,"Āpūrati yaso tassa[ tassa yeso( bahūsu, vinayepi)], sukkapakkheva[ juṇhapakkheva( ka.)] candimā’’ ti. "
365073,95,918,2,3,1,16,2,Cha apāyamukhāni 
