368099,96,315,19,40,1,158,16,Ayaṃ panettha attho– mahāsattañhi‘‘ himavantaṃ ajjhogāhetvā ajja dhammikapabbataṃ pavisissāmī’’ ti nikkhantaṃ disvā sakko devānamindo vissakammadevaputtaṃ āmantesi–
