368106,96,318,2,3,1,3,1,Āha . 
368107,96,318,4,11,1,42,7,Tattha assamo sukato mayhan ti sukato mayā. 
368108,96,318,12,20,1,58,7,Paṇṇasālā {sumāpitā}ti paṇṇacchannā sālāpi me sumāpitā ahosi. 
368109,96,319,2,16,1,120,10,"Pañcadosavivajjitan ti pañcime caṅkamadosā nāma thaddhavisamatā, antorukkhatā, gahanacchannatā, atisambādhatā, ativisālatāti. "
368110,96,319,17,33,1,133,13,"Thaddhavisamabhūmibhāgasmiñhi caṅkame caṅkamantassa pādā rujjanti, phoṭā uṭṭhahanti, cittaṃ ekaggataṃ na labhati, kammaṭṭhānaṃ vipajjati. "
368111,96,319,34,40,1,61,6,Mudusamatale pana phāsuvihāraṃ āgamma kammaṭṭhānaṃ sampajjati. 
