369964,96,1055,2,8,1,69,6,Vacīkammadvārakathāyaṃ pana cetanāviratisaddavasena tividhā vācā nāma. 
369965,96,1055,9,41,1,114,16,"Tattha‘‘ catūhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgatā vācā subhāsitā hoti no dubbhāsitā, anavajjā ca ananuvajjā ca viññūnan’’ ti( saṃ. ni.1.213); "
369966,96,1055,42,45,1,20,3,ayaṃ cetanāvācā nāma. 
369967,96,1055,46,71,1,88,13,"Yā‘‘ catūhi vacīduccaritehi ārati virati… pe… ayaṃ vuccati sammāvācā’’ ti( vibha.206), ayaṃ virativācā nāma."
369968,96,1055,72,96,1,84,12,"‘‘ Vācā girā byappatho udīraṇaṃ ghoso ghosakammaṃ vācā vacībhedo’’ ti( dha. sa.850), ayaṃ saddavācā nāma. "
369969,96,1055,97,105,1,55,8,Tāsu vacīkammadvāran ti neva cetanāya nāmaṃ na viratiyā. 
369970,96,1055,106,115,1,59,8,"Sahasaddā pana ekā viññatti atthi, idaṃ vacīkammadvāraṃ nāma. "
369971,96,1055,116,119,1,19,3,Yaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ–
369972,96,1055,120,126,1,30,4,‘‘ katamaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ vacīviññatti? 
369973,96,1055,127,146,1,139,18,"Yā kusalacittassa vā akusalacittassa vā abyākatacittassa vā vācā girā byappatho udīraṇaṃ ghoso ghosakammaṃ vācā vacībhedo, ayaṃ vuccati vācā. "
369974,96,1055,147,168,1,78,11,"Yā tāya vācāya viññatti viññāpanā viññāpitattaṃ, idaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ vacīviññattī’’ ti( dha. sa.636)."
369975,96,1056,2,14,1,81,11,‘ Idaṃ vakkhāmi etaṃ vakkhāmī’ ti hi vitakkayato vitakkavipphārasaddo nāma uppajjati. 
369976,96,1056,15,21,1,59,6,Ayaṃ na sotaviññeyyo manoviññeyyoti mahāaṭṭhakathāyaṃ āgato. 
369977,96,1056,22,33,1,119,9,Āgamaṭṭhakathāsu pana‘ vitakkavipphārasaddan’ ti vitakkavipphāravasena uppannaṃ vippalapantānaṃ suttappamattādīnaṃ saddaṃ;
369978,96,1056,34,47,1,57,10,"‘ sutvā’ ti taṃ sutvā, yaṃ vitakkayato tassa so saddo uppanno; "
369979,96,1056,48,64,1,84,13,"tassa vasena‘ evampi te mano, itthampi te mano’ ti ādisatīti vatvā vatthūnipi kathitāni. "
369980,96,1056,65,77,1,91,8,Paṭṭhānepi‘‘ cittasamuṭṭhānaṃ saddāyatanaṃ sotaviññāṇassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo’’ ti āgataṃ. 
369981,96,1056,78,87,1,88,8,Tasmā vinā viññattighaṭṭanāya uppajjamāno asotaviññeyyo vitakkavipphārasaddo nāma natthi.
369982,96,1056,88,111,1,147,19,‘ Idaṃ vakkhāmi etaṃ vakkhāmī’ ti uppajjamānaṃ pana cittaṃ pathavīdhātu āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātu vaṇṇo gandho raso ojāti aṭṭha rūpāni samuṭṭhāpeti. 
369983,96,1056,112,119,1,82,7,Tesaṃ abbhantare cittasamuṭṭhānā pathavīdhātu upādinnakaṃ ghaṭṭayamānāva uppajjati. 
369984,96,1056,120,125,1,48,5,Tena dhātusaṅghaṭṭanena saheva saddo uppajjatīti. 
369985,96,1056,126,129,1,30,3,Ayaṃ cittasamuṭṭhānasaddo nāma. 
369986,96,1056,130,133,1,16,3,Ayaṃ na viññatti. 
369987,96,1056,134,147,1,123,12,"Tassā pana cittasamuṭṭhānāya pathavīdhātuyā upādinnakaghaṭṭanassa paccayabhūto eko ākāravikāro atthi, ayaṃ vacīviññatti nāma. "
369988,96,1056,148,160,1,93,12,Ito paraṃ sā aṭṭha rūpāni viya na cittasamuṭṭhānātiādi sabbaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayeneva veditabbaṃ. 
