369990,96,1057,27,34,1,59,7,Kāyaviññatti viya ca ayampi tiracchānagatānampi pākaṭā hoti.
369991,96,1057,35,57,1,107,17,"‘ Ehi, yāhī’ ti hi saddaṃ sutvā tiracchānagatāpi‘ idaṃ nāmesa kāreti maññe’ ti ñatvā āgacchanti ceva gacchanti ca. "
